      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/gold-steadies-with-focus-on-key-us-data-and-election-endgame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员为关键数据做准备，黄金价格向纪录高位迈进，这些数据将有助于为美联储下次政策决定奠定基础，而美国总统大选的倒计时仍在继续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/gold-steadies-with-focus-on-key-us-data-and-election-endgame</guid>
